url: https://mida.cartodb.com/api/v2/sql?format=GeoJSON&q=SELECT cartodb_id, status, to_date(startdato, 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MI:SS') as startdato, to_date(reel_slutdato, 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MI:SS') as slutdato, vejnavn, type, tilladelsesnr,sagsbeh_navn,the_geom FROM vm_tilladelser_2 WHERE type IN ('Grave') AND type IS NOT NULL AND status IN ('Godkendt') AND status IS NOT NULL AND the_geom IS NOT NULL AND to_date(reel_slutdato,'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MI:SS') > now()

https://mida.cartodb.com/api/v2/sql?format=GeoJSON&q=SELECT cartodb_id, adgangsadresse_dawa_start,forventet_deltagerantal_max,forventet_deltagerantal_samlet,plotaroute_url,startpunkt, name,name_id, subject_routename as subject, workflow_title AS status, TO_CHAR(arrangementets_starttidspunkt, 'YYYY-MM-DD\"T\"HH:MI:SS') as startdato, TO_CHAR(arrangementets_sluttidspunkt, 'YYYY-MM-DD\"T\"HH:MI:SS') as slutdato, ref, agent_name,category_title, the_geom FROM arrangementsruter WHERE hide IN ('Unchecked') AND workflow_title IN ('Ansøgning godkendt','Ansøgning indsendt','Ansøgning under behandling','Ansøgning forhåndsgodkendt') AND workflow_title IS NOT NULL AND arrangementets_sluttidspunkt > now()

https://mida.cartodb.com/api/v2/sql?format=GeoJSON&q=SELECT cartodb_id, status, to_date(startdato, 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MI:SS') %2B interval '1 day' as startdato, to_date(reel_slutdato, 'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MI:SS') %2B interval '1 day' as slutdato, vejnavn, type, tilladelsesnr,sagsbeh_navn,the_geom FROM vm_tilladelser_2 WHERE type IN ('Materiel') AND type IS NOT NULL AND status IN ('Godkendt') AND status IS NOT NULL AND the_geom IS NOT NULL AND to_date(reel_slutdato,'YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MI:SS') > now()
